    "rationale": "Credibility assessment reviewed by the V&V 40 assessment team. Seven of thirteen factors were assessed; all assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors were not assessed and represent epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the package is formally accepted for submission to illustrate the W-ON-02 weakness: the ContextOfUse specifies no applicability constraints and no operating envelope, leaving the model's valid range of use unspecified and the credibility boundary undefined.",
